title: Wall Street Breakfast: The Week Ahead
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: The Federal Reserve is expected to raise interest rates as it continues to try to stem rising inflation. While investors are edgy on the retail sector, Kroger (KR) could still come out on top with its earnings report this week. Universal’s Jurassic World: Dominion (NASDAQ:CMCSA) has jumped to the forefront of the summer box office battle.
